    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/240a7dfccb5e733342507e896ab68a90_4399266908858661795.png",
                "id": "talent25365",
                "key": "Ancient Sword Art",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Ancient Sword Art"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Memanggil<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\"> Herald of Frost</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/2575ddfaacc7015ebab2d17fba4593ea_6310501579530120259.png",
                "id": "talent94181",
                "key": "Adeptus Art: Herald of Frost",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptus Art: Herald of Frost"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span> dan menciptakan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fortune-Preserving Talisman</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Fortune-Preserving Talisman</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status Pertempuran</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karaktermu menggunakan Skill:</span> Jika Karakter tersebut HP-nya tidak penuh, maka akan memulihkan 2 poin HP kepada Karakter tersebut. </p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/900dec327166a00218479cf8616072fc_6768554446210277569.png",
                "id": "talent22997",
                "key": "Adeptus Art: Preserver of Fortune",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Adeptus Art: Preserver of Fortune"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Panggilan</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Tahap Selesai:</span> Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat panggilan ini berada dalam arena, jika Qiqi menggunakan Normal Attack:</span> memulihkan 1 poin HP kepada Karaktermu yang telah menerima DMG paling banyak. Sekali setiap Ronde: memulihkan lagi 1 poin HP Karakter aktifmu.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_7339106588845516191.png",
                "id": "talent16730",
                "key": "Herald of Frost",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_7524355754600056394.png",
                "title": "Herald of Frost"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Cryo dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Melt</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Frozen</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, target tidak dapat melangkah di Ronde ini (Dapat dihapus di muka setelah target menerima Physical DMG atau Pyro DMG, namun DMG +2)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_6895263067055288123.png",
                "id": "talent20459",
                "key": "Cryo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Cryo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.<br><br><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_8910636203164743934.png",
                "id": "talent76585",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
